when casted on enemys they will be set Aflame, taking 8 plus 30% of Davion strenght in magical damage every 0.4 second that last 4 second
and Davion will get heal by 85% of the damage done with Holy Fire, and if Holy Light is casted on Davion he will become a Fire Crusade
becoming immune to all slow and having 12% damage reduction and also increasing his movespeed by 24% for 3.5 second


